node.text:
New price! Take another look at my epic listing in Guard gated Hidden Hills, Ca. The crown jewel of this prestigious equestrian community. Set behind private gates and atop 7.5 usable acres with explosive panoramic views! Completed in 2019, this 15,000 square foot contemporary farmhouse boasts every amenity desired. Features include a private two hole par 3 golf course, north/south tennis court, sand volleyball court, barn, zero edge infinity pool and much more. Interior features include a theater, gym, office, elevator, an abundance of pocket doors and much more. This is the ultimate in Southern California living! A perfect 10!

$27,500,000

New listing! Fired up to launch this completely reimagined contemporary French masterpiece in Westlake Village, Ca. Extraordinary 8400 square foot showplace atop over 2.2 acres with explosive panoramic views. Premier location behind private gates in the prestigious guard gated community, North Ranch Country Club Estates. This magnificent estate has recently undergone a complete renovation designed and built with the absolute finest finishes. Everything is new and truly special. An all new open concept floorplan boasts a massive double island kitchen, theater, office /library, second story loft/bonus area, gym, elevator and much more. The resort quality grounds boast an infinity pool, all new outdoor kitchen, covered pavilion, manicured lawns, and a new winding pathway to a massive orchard and room for possible tennis court. All with complete privacy and views. A very special offering!

$7,500,000

node.text:
Great way to end the week! Grateful to close escrow on this brand new modern craftsman in Westlake Village, Ca.  I am super excited to say that we are now sold out of Phase 2 of The Estates At North Ranch! With phase 3 under construction, I look forward to representing the final 5 sensational estates in 2022! This one was special. Over an acre of usable grounds with panoramic views! Big thanks to my friend and colleague @karenhawkins1 for bringing the terrific buyers. Another wonderful family to add to this extraordinary brand new gated community. Big thanks to @prolinemortgage and Sean Casey for securing the financing on this deal. The Estates At North Ranch is Ventura County’s hottest community with 10 recent closings. I’m honored to be the exclusive agent for the development. The community is developed by my lifelong friend @ronlogan123 with each residence designed by @sophieidan and masterfully built by top luxury builders @adroitcustomhomes ! A fantastic team that I’m incredibly grateful to be a part of!

Sold for $5,495,000

node.text:
Grateful to close escrow today on this Oak Park traditional. This one was special for me and my family because it was OUR  home. We lived in this wonderful home and community for the past 19 years and have nothing but wonderful memories. Funny, when sellers tell me that they are emotional about selling their homes,  I always smile but never pay much attention. That will change moving forward because it is emotional. I decided to bring on a “co-listing” agent because I wanted to separate myself a bit from from the transaction. I brought on a great young realtor who happens to be close  friends with my son. Thank you  @brandoncoppel for all your help! You did a fantastic job! I also want to thank my friends and colleagues @theshevins for bringing such fantastic buyers. A true pleasure and pain free deal. We had 14 offers in the first two days and selected great people to start a new chapter in the home we loved. 

Sold for $2,425,000

There is also a barn with 4 stall breezeway, custom pool and spa and a fenced arena with full size team penning/roping and sand arena. This is truly an awe inspiring ranch with every amenity desired.
